        <mxCell id="sr3Lcem74erj5iztOOXT-7" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;This diagram defines the core financial lifecycle and operational constraints of the banking system. It emphasizes security and business logic by &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;146&quot;&gt;including&lt;/b&gt; &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;156&quot;&gt;Verify Identity&lt;/code&gt; for all sensitive actions (&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;199&quot;&gt;Transfer Funds&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;215&quot;&gt;View Account Info&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;234&quot;&gt;View Transaction History&lt;/code&gt;) and mandating a &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;276&quot;&gt;Check Balance&lt;/code&gt; during funds movement. Additionally, it features an &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;342&quot;&gt;extend&lt;/b&gt; relationship where &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;368&quot;&gt;Send Notification&lt;/code&gt; serves as an optional post-transaction task. The model clearly delineates the roles of the &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;477&quot;&gt;Customer&lt;/b&gt;, who manages personal assets, and the &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;524&quot;&gt;Bank Admin&lt;/b&gt;, who oversees system-wide functions like rate updates and transaction auditing.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;137&quot;&gt;Key Actors:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;149&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Customer, Bank Admin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt; " vertex="1">
